{"tid":1077514,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"支那豪：我不是故意踢人的","createTime":"2019-03-25T15:30:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-25T16:00:56.000Z","uid":42396,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"92575d3cf6780c4fc15c68fb4dc6d1e7334858db","tid":1077514,"uid":42396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T15:30:41.000Z","msg":"魏世豪在比賽結束後的採訪中說，他的犯規不是故意的。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;我認為這是犯規。我們只是沒有接觸球超過十分鐘。我們使用戰術犯規來減慢比賽速度。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;我不知道他是什麼，足球不可避免地是不可避免的。我不是故意的。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n同西班牙蝗狗好似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c6a5f2ec7fc1aeb7848806e94e67ed7b6d253cb","tid":1077514,"uid":42396,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T15:33:18.000Z","msg":"掂唔到波就要收人山<br />\n巴塞曼城去到點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03b71c7f49504786349e52e449428704d563cc61","tid":1077514,"uid":67957,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T15:42:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4Rm8bvn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4Rm8bvn.png&h=4411ee77&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e20a972680da69b7c2f8bbb452b4a439b15b6824","tid":1077514,"uid":133756,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T15:43:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsimgs.sina.tw/article/images/news-15535216194117.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsimgs.sina.tw%2Farticle%2Fimages%2Fnews-15535216194117.jpg&h=cd69cc27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n收數定道歉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1b0750bc5e336d95098bdc14b9965c78154a0ec","tid":1077514,"uid":61271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T15:45:30.000Z","msg":"同支那人踢波真係好危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"h